data.text:
2014 AVN Unsung Starlet of the Year

Presley Hart got her start in the business in 2011 and landed her breakout role as the lead in Jim Powers' 2012 production Diary of Love (Smash Pictures), a XXX homage to one of her favorite films, The Notebook. That performance garnered her a Best Actress nod in the 2013 AVN Awards race, and shortly thereafter, she was named the Penthouse Pet of the Month for the March 2013 issue.

Presley started 2014 off with an even bigger bang, not only winning her first AVN Award for Unsung Starlet of the Year, but making the cover of Elegant Angel Productions' Best New Starlets 2014, the studio's annual ode to the hottest up-and-comers in the business.

Find Presley Hart on Twitter @PresleyHartXXX.
